#: operations/common/threshold.c:28
msgid "Lowest value to be included."
msgstr "ຄ່າຕໍ່າສຸດທີ່ຈະລວມເຂົ້າ."

#: operations/common/threshold.c:33
msgid "Highest value to be included as white."
msgstr "ຄ່າສູງສຸດທີ່ຈະລວມເຂົ້າເປັນສີຂາວ."

#: operations/common/threshold.c:169
msgid ""
"Thresholds the image to white/black based on either the global values set in "
"the value (low) and high properties, or per pixel from the aux input."
msgstr ""
"ກໍານົດຄ່າເກນຂອງພາບເປັນສີຂາວ/ດໍາ ໂດຍອີງໃສ່ຄ່າທົ່ວໄປທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຄຸນສົມບັດຄ່າ (ຕໍ່າ) ແລະ ສູງ, ຫຼື ຕາມແຕ່ລະພິກເຊລຈາກຕົ້ນສະບັບເສີມ."

#: operations/common/tile.c:24
msgid "Horizontal offset"
msgstr "ໄລຍະຫ່າງແນວນອນ"

#: operations/common/tile.c:29
msgid "Vertical offset"
msgstr "ໄລຍະຫ່າງແນວຕັ້ງ"

#: operations/common/tile.c:159
msgid "Tile"
msgstr "ຕໍ່ກັນ"

#: operations/common/tile.c:165
msgid "Infinitely repeats the input image."
msgstr "ເຮັດຊໍ້າພາບຕົ້ນສະບັບຢ່າງບໍ່ສິ້ນສຸດ."

#: operations/common/tile-seamless.c:212
msgid "Make Seamlessly tileable"
msgstr "ເຮັດໃຫ້ສາມາດຕໍ່ກັນໄດ້ຢ່າງລຽບນຽນ"

#: operations/common/tile-seamless.c:216
msgid ""
"Make the input buffer seamlessly tileable. The algorithm is not content-"
"aware, so the result may need post-processing."
msgstr ""
"ເຮັດໃຫ້ບັບເຟີຕົ້ນສະບັບສາມາດຕໍ່ກັນໄດ້ຢ່າງລຽບນຽນ. ອັນກໍຣິທຶມບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບຮູ້ເນື້ອຫາ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນຜົນລັບອາດຈະຕ້ອງການການປະມວນຜົນເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

#: operations/common/unpremultiply.c:78
msgid "Unpremultiply alpha"
msgstr "ຍົກເລີກການຄູນອັນຟາລ່ວງໜ້າ"

#: operations/common/unpremultiply.c:80
msgid ""
"Unpremultiplies a buffer that contains pre-multiplied colors (but according "
"to the babl format is not.)"
msgstr "ຍົກເລີກການຄູນລ່ວງໜ້າຂອງບັບເຟີທີ່ບັນຈຸສີທີ່ຖືກຄູນລ່ວງໜ້າ (ແຕ່ຕາມຮູບແບບ babl ແມ່ນບໍ່ໄດ້ເປັນ.)"

#: operations/common/unsharp-mask.c:25
msgid "Expressed as standard deviation, in pixels"
msgstr "ສະແດງເປັນຄ່າຜັນປ່ຽນມາດຕະຖານ, ເປັນພິກເຊລ"

#: operations/common/unsharp-mask.c:32
msgid "Scaling factor for unsharp-mask, the strength of effect"
msgstr "ໂຕຄູນຂະໜາດສໍາລັບໜ້າກາກບໍ່ຄົມ, ຄວາມແຮງຂອງເອັບເຟັກ"

#: operations/common/unsharp-mask.c:144
msgid "Sharpen (Unsharp Mask)"
msgstr "ເພີ່ມຄວາມຄົມຊັດ (ໜ້າກາກບໍ່ຄົມ)"

#: operations/common/unsharp-mask.c:147
msgid ""
"Sharpen image, by adding difference to blurred image, a technique for "
"sharpening originally used in darkrooms."
msgstr ""
"ເຮັດໃຫ້ພາບຄົມຊັດ, ໂດຍການເພີ່ມຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງໃສ່ພາບທີ່ເບລີ, ເປັນເຕັກນິກສໍາລັບການເພີ່ມຄວາມຄົມຊັດທີ່ເຄີຍໃຊ້ໃນຫ້ອງມືດ."

#: operations/common/value-invert.c:149
msgid "Value Invert"
msgstr "ປີ້ນຄ່າ"

#: operations/common/value-invert.c:153
msgid ""
"Invert the value component, the result has the brightness inverted, keeping "
"the color."
msgstr "ປີ້ນອົງປະກອບຄ່າ, ຜົນລັບຈະມີຄວາມສະຫວ່າງປີ້ນກັບ, ແຕ່ຍັງຮັກສາສີໄວ້ຄືເກົ່າ."

#: operations/common/vignette.c:32
msgid "Vignette shape"
msgstr "ຮູບຮ່າງວິນເຍດ"

#. TRANSLATORS: the string 'black' should not be translated
#: operations/common/vignette.c:38
msgid ""
"Defaults to 'black', you can use transparency here to erase portions of an "
"image"
msgstr "ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 'ສີດໍາ', ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ຄວາມໂປ່ງໃສຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້ເພື່ອລຶບບາງສ່ວນຂອງພາບ"

#: operations/common/vignette.c:41
msgid "How far out vignetting goes as portion of half image diagonal"
msgstr "ໄລຍະທີ່ວິນເຍດອອກໄປເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງເຄິ່ງເສັ້ນຂວາງຂອງພາບ"

#: operations/common/vignette.c:49 operations/common-cxx/piecewise-blend.cc:33
msgid "Gamma"
msgstr "ແກມມາ"

#: operations/common/vignette.c:50
msgid "Falloff linearity"
msgstr "ຄວາມເປັນເສັ້ນຊື່ຂອງການຈາງລົງ"

#: operations/common/vignette.c:54
msgid "Proportion"
msgstr "ສັດສ່ວນ"

#: operations/common/vignette.c:55
msgid "How close we are to image proportions"
msgstr "ຄວາມໃກ້ຄຽງກັບສັດສ່ວນຂອງພາບ"

#: operations/common/vignette.c:58
msgid "Squeeze"
msgstr "ບີບ"

#: operations/common/vignette.c:59
msgid ""
"Aspect ratio to use, -0.5 = 1:2, 0.0 = 1:1, 0.5 = 2:1, -1.0 = 1:inf 1.0 = "
"inf:1, this is applied after proportion is taken into account, to directly "
"use squeeze factor as proportions, set proportion to 0.0."
